{
  "number": 86,
  "name": "At-Taariq",
  "arabicName": "سُورَةُ الطَّارِقِ",
  "revelationType": "Meccan",
  "totalAyahs": 17,
  "translator": "Saheeh International",
  "edition": "en.sahih",
  "language": "English",
  "ayahs": [
    {
      "number": 1,
      "text": "By the sky and the night comer -",
      "ayah_number": 1,
      "verse_key": "86:1"
    },
    {
      "number": 2,
      "text": "And what can make you know what is the night comer?",
      "ayah_number": 2,
      "verse_key": "86:2"
    },
    {
      "number": 3,
      "text": "It is the piercing star -",
      "ayah_number": 3,
      "verse_key": "86:3"
    },
    {
      "number": 4,
      "text": "There is no soul but that it has over it a protector.",
      "ayah_number": 4,
      "verse_key": "86:4"
    },
    {
      "number": 5,
      "text": "So let man observe from what he was created.",
      "ayah_number": 5,
      "verse_key": "86:5"
    },
    {
      "number": 6,
      "text": "He was created from a fluid, ejected,",
      "ayah_number": 6,
      "verse_key": "86:6"
    },
    {
      "number": 7,
      "text": "Emerging from between the backbone and the ribs.",
      "ayah_number": 7,
      "verse_key": "86:7"
    },
    {
      "number": 8,
      "text": "Indeed, Allah, to return him [to life], is Able.",
      "ayah_number": 8,
      "verse_key": "86:8"
    },
    {
      "number": 9,
      "text": "The Day when secrets will be put on trial,",
      "ayah_number": 9,
      "verse_key": "86:9"
    },
    {
      "number": 10,
      "text": "Then man will have no power or any helper.",
      "ayah_number": 10,
      "verse_key": "86:10"
    },
    {
      "number": 11,
      "text": "By the sky which returns [rain]",
      "ayah_number": 11,
      "verse_key": "86:11"
    },
    {
      "number": 12,
      "text": "And [by] the earth which cracks open,",
      "ayah_number": 12,
      "verse_key": "86:12"
    },
    {
      "number": 13,
      "text": "Indeed, the Qur'an is a decisive statement,",
      "ayah_number": 13,
      "verse_key": "86:13"
    },
    {
      "number": 14,
      "text": "And it is not amusement.",
      "ayah_number": 14,
      "verse_key": "86:14"
    },
    {
      "number": 15,
      "text": "Indeed, they are planning a plan,",
      "ayah_number": 15,
      "verse_key": "86:15"
    },
    {
      "number": 16,
      "text": "But I am planning a plan.",
      "ayah_number": 16,
      "verse_key": "86:16"
    },
    {
      "number": 17,
      "text": "So allow time for the disbelievers. Leave them awhile.",
      "ayah_number": 17,
      "verse_key": "86:17"
    }
  ]
}